---
import Image from "astro/components/Image.astro";
import profile from "public/images/profile_picture.jpg";
import InstagramIcon from "@components/icons/InstagramIcon.astro";
import GitHubIcon from "@components/icons/GitHubIcon.astro";
import ChevronsDownIcon from "@components/icons/ChevronsDownIcon.astro";
---

<header class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-8 w-full">
    <div
        class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-8 lg:gap-12 w-full h-screen"
    >
        <!-- IMAGE -->
        <picture class="aspect-[3/4] w-72 md:w-4/12 rounded-lg bg-slate-500">
            <Image
                src={profile}
                alt="Mi foto de perfil"
                class="w-full h-full aspect-[3/4] rounded-lg object-cover"
            />
        </picture>

        <!-- iINFO -->
        <article class="flex flex-col justify-center gap-4 w-full md:w-8/12">
            <h2
                class="flex flex-col text-2xl sm:text-3xl lg:text-5xl font-bold"
            >
                Hola!, soy
                <span>
                    <span
                        class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-pink-500 via-violet-500 to-sky-500"
                        >Nizvan Monteón Ricárdez</span
                    >
                    🚀
                </span>
            </h2>

            <p
                class="text-sm sm:text-base font-extralight text-white/85 max-w-[640px]"
            >
                Soy un chico de 23 años, vivo en Oaxaca, Méixco, y soy Ingeniero
                en Sistemas Computacionales. Amo programar, me encanta resolver
                problemas y soy un apasionado por el diseño. Siempre practico
                hasta mejorar en todo lo que me proponga, gracias a mi
                entusiasmo por aprender cosas nuevas.
            </p>

            <div class="flex gap-4 items-center mt-4">
                <a
                    href="https://github.com/Nizvan018"
                    target="_blank"
                    rel="noopener noreferer"
                    class="opacity-50 duration-200 hover:opacity-100"
                >
                    <GitHubIcon width={24} height={24} />
                </a>
                <a
                    href="https://www.instagram.com/nizvan_dev/"
                    target="_blank"
                    rel="noopener noreferer"
                    class="opacity-50 duration-200 hover:opacity-100"
                >
                    <InstagramIcon width={24} height={24} />
                </a>
                <span class="text-sm opacity-50 duration-200 hover:opacity-100"
                    >nizvan.dev@gmail.com</span
                >
            </div>
        </article>
    </div>
    <a href="" class="flex flex-col items-center gap-2 h-24 cursor-pointer">
        <span class="text-sm sm:text-base">Conóceme un poquito más</span>
        <ChevronsDownIcon className="animate-bounce" />
    </a>
</header>

<style>
    header {
        height: calc(100vh - 64px);
    }
</style>
